Thunderbirds Are Go - S01E012 Under Pressure AVC AAC {OJ}

Reboot of the classic children's adventure series. A heavy metal extraction platform carrying toxic waste at the bottom of the ocean is in trouble. Gordon rushes in with 

Thunderbird 4 when a fire on board the rolling factory damages its steering capabilities. With the help of Lady Penelope and Parker on the surface, Gordon must rescue platform 

operator Ned Tedford and prevent the rig from spilling its waste. AD SUB
